               <msContents>
                  <summary>Computus, ባሕረ፡ ሐሳብ፡; Five Pillars of Mystery, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡; Beauty of Creation, ሥነ፡ ፍጥረት፡; Homily on Benefits for all, ለሁሉ፡ የሚጠቅም፡ ነገረ፡ ምዕዳን፡; On the burial of the faithful, በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡ በርትዕት፡ ሃይማኖት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="29v" facs="005">Fols 1r–29v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3851Hassab">We have written a
                                                  computus that we will remember in order not to
                                                  congregate with apostates...</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="1r" to="10v" facs="005">Fols 1r–10v</locus>
                        <title>Introduction, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መቅድም። </foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ከዚህም ቀጥለን(sic)፡ የድሜጥሮስን፡ ነገር፡ ሐሳበ፡ ባሕርን፡ እንናገራለን። ባሕረ፡ ሐሳብም ይላል። ሐሳበ፡ ባሕር፡ አለ፡ የዘመን፡ ቁጽር፡ ሲል፡ ነው። ባሕረ፡ ሐሳብ፡ አለ፡ ቁጽር፡ ያለው ዘመን፡ ሲል፡ ነው፡ ባሕርን፡ ዘመን፡ ሲል፡ የት፡ ይገኛል፡ ቢሉ፡ እስመ፡ በመዳልው፡ ደለወ፡ ኩሉ፡ ዓለመ፡ ወበመስፈርት፡ ሰፈራ፡ ለባሕር፡ ብሏል፡ ሄኖክ። <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="10v" to="15r" facs="015">Fols 10v–15r</locus>
                        <title>Computus of the feast and fast days of the Gospel, <foreign xml:lang="gez">በዓላተ፡ ወንጌል፡ አጽዋማተ፡ ወንጌል፡ </foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዓለም፡ ከተፈጠረ፡ ዘመን፡ ከተቆጠረ፡ ፯ሽህ፡ ካ፬፻፴፯ ሆነ፡ በዘመነ፡ ዮሐንስ። ለዚህም፡ መስፈሪያ፡ መቁጸሪያ፡ ፰ አዕዋዳት፡ አሉት። <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="15v" to="20v" facs="020">Fols 15v–20v</locus>
                        <title>Computus of Old Testament, <foreign xml:lang="gez">በዓላተ፡ ኦሪት፡ አጽዋማተ፡ ኦሪት፡ </foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ከዚህም ቀጥለን፡ አጽዋማተ፡ ኦሪትን፡ በዓላተ፡ ኦሪትን፡ እንናገራለን፡ አጽዋማተ፡ ኦሪት፡ በዓላተ፡ ኦሪት፡ ስንት፡ ናቸው፡ ቢሉ፡ ፰ ናቸው። <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="20v" to="23v" facs="025">Fols 20v–23v</locus>
                        <title>On hours of day and night, <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ሰዓታተ፡ መዓልት፡ ወሌሊት፡ </foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወዓዲ፡ ንነግር፡ በእንተ፡ ሰዓታተ፡ መዓልት፡ ወሌሊት፡ ዘከመ፡ የዓዱ፡ ለለወርኁ። ቀዊመከ፡ ርቱዓ፡ ትኔጽር፡ ጽላሎተ፡ ርእሰከ፡ ወትትኤመር፡ እስከ፡ ኀበ፡ በጽሐ። <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="23v" to="29v" facs="028">Fols 23v–29v</locus>
                        <title>On the Beginning  of Fast days, <foreign xml:lang="gez">በአተ፡ ጾም፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="30r" to="37r" facs="034">Fols 30r–37r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿǝmāda
                                                  mǝśṭir</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="am">Amharic</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="37v" to="40r" facs="042">Fols 37v–40r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2314senafe">Śǝna fǝṭrat (General
                                                  record)</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="40r" to="41r" facs="044">Fols 40r–41r</locus>
                     <title>Homily on Benefits for all, ለሁሉ፡ የሚጠቅም፡ ነገረ፡ ምዕዳን፡</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="41r" to="44r" facs="045">Fols 41r–44r</locus>
                     <title>On the burial of the faithful, በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡ በርትዕት፡ ሃይማኖት፡</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ ኑዛዜ፡ ለኅዙናን፡ ወለትኩዛን፡ በእንተ፡ እለ፡ ኖሙ፡ በርትዕት፡ ሃይማኖት፡ በጸናች፡ በቀናች፡ ተዋህዶ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ለሚሞቱ ሰዎች ሁሉ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
